      "width": 380,
      "height": 190,
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "3️⃣ Diagram Generation\n\n• Trigger: Push *.excalidraw\n• Trigger: Manual dispatch\n• Install excalidraw-export-cli\n• Install Playwright browsers\n• Convert: .excalidraw → .png\n• Git pull --rebase\n• Commit & push PNGs\n• Skip if: no changes",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
